Package de.ingogriebsch.spring.hateoas.siren

Siren-specific extensions, SPIs and Jackson customizations.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CollectionModelFactory
    Factory to create a CollectionModel instance based on the given input evaluated during deserialization.
    EntityModelFactory
    Factory to create a EntityModel instance based on the given input evaluated during deserialization.
    PagedModelFactory
    Factory to create a PagedModel instance based on the given input evaluated during deserialization.
    RepresentationModelFactories
    Holds factories for all known types of RepresentationModels to be used during the deserialization process.
    RepresentationModelFactory
    Factory to create a RepresentationModel instance based on the given input evaluated during deserialization.
    SirenEntityClassProvider
    API to provide information about the nature of the content of a Siren entity.
    SirenEntityRelProvider
    API to provide information about the relationship of a Siren entity to it's parent.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MediaTypes
    Constants for the Siren hypermedia type.
    SirenConfiguration
    Siren specific configuration.
    SirenLinkDiscoverer
    LinkDiscoverer implementation based on Siren link structure.
    SirenModelBuilder
    Builder which allows to build complex Siren entity structures.
